data.value: This is the future of colonization for humans is to create a moon base city.Thiscity will help start another colonization of another planet called Mars. It willalso procide logistical support to the planet inorder to make life in Mars Sustainable.Their wil be three types of structered domes that will be 3D printedin prepareof the colonization. The small dome will house the colonizers, the medium-sized domes will be where the colonizers work, food, and medical needs.The main dome(center) will be the moonbase city adn act as an airport main for transporting humasn either frrom/to Mars or from/to Earth.
